\s Wachunga walilinda kundi
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Wachunga walilinda kundi lao kwa usiku\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Tazama, malaika aliwatokea mbio.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na utukufu wake Bwana ukawaangazia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Wakaogopa sana wakiona nuru ile.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na malaika yake Bwana akawaambia, \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Musiogope,\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd kwani ninakuja na habari.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Habari Njema ya furaha itakayokuwa Kwa watu wote wa dunia ninaleta kwenu.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Amezaliwa leo tu kwa muji wa Daudi Mwokozi ndiye Kristo Bwana, kwa ajili Yesu.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Na hii alama kwenu mutamwona kwa kizizi, Amelalishwa kwa sanduku ya kulisha nyama.\bd*\bd ”\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Kwa gaf\bd*\bd ’\bd*\bd la makutano ya majeshi ya\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni Walizunguka malaika wakisifu \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd .\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd “\bd*\bd Ee \bd*\bd Utukufu \bd*\bd kwake \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd , kule kwa\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Salama duniani kwa wanaomupendeza\bd*\bd .”\bd*
